title: Israel’s Tech Companies Are Fighting Netanyahu—or Leaving the Startup Nation
description: As protests rage over Israel’s controversial reforms to the supreme court, many tech companies have been moving their money and headquarters offshore.

title: Meta’s Open Source Llama Upsets the AI Horse Race
description: Meta is giving its answer to OpenAI’s GPT-4 away for free. The move could intensify the generative AI boom by making it easier for entrepreneurs to build powerful new AI systems.
